      "writtenOn": "2016-09-19T17:13:06Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Can metrics values be uint32_t, which is what we use for minidump exception codes?\n\nIf metrics only provides for unsigned int, then it’s right to stick with that.",
      "revId": "07da507b2466afb52a00804d196f57eba59bf126",
